        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Qi Yue, a carefree rich girl, learns from her future son, Qi Shuo, that she is destined for an unhappy marriage. To change her fate, Qi Shuo travels back in time to guide her. Discovering her future husband is the brilliant Lu Xiao, Qi Yue works to improve herself. Under Qi Shuo’s transformation plan, she gets into the same university as Lu Xiao and relentlessly pursues him. With Qi Shuo’s help, her\n\npersistence and charm eventually win Lu Xiao’s heart.",
